divs: Sighting Detailson the way to a store i took a pic of the moon last year. and a few days ago i was looking at the pic, deciding whether or not to discard the pic. that's when i noticed the two lights in the corner of the pic. could these be stars? or a part of a constilation? or is this a UFO? i dont know.. i think i was abducted a week before my 23rd BDay in June this year.. i had a reeeeeeally weird 'dream' and then i woke up with a burn on my left eyeball. a deep burn. a few friends pointed out that it looked like it was in the shape of a left eyeball.. so i did some research and it turns out that the Sumerian people used to use a left eyeball symbol for the Alien God Nanna, the Alien God of the moon...
